The three-day introductory course for future glaciers has had a great success and attracted visitors from all over the world.
Special courses on chocolate ice are also offered and over several days. Similarly, practical sessions are organized in the private ice cream.
In the midst of the midst of the midlife, a number of people dream of a new career, others are simply at risk of realizing their burning desire on smooth ice.
